kpi_info.title: The average call setup time of the durations of the external released connections
kpi_info.use: The average call setup time of the durations of the external released connections during the period. Clear code range for internal failure released connection: 800...BFF. The unit of measure is seconds in ASCII reports and 10 milliseconds in XML reports.
